Problem: Try to write the requirements for simple arcade style driving game where the player has to navigate around obstacles to keep from crashing.

1. There must be a sprite for the player to control
2. There must be different obstacles for the player to avoid
3. There has to be different levels for the player to play in
4. The levels should get more difficult as they go on to provide a challenge
5. The player should be able to pick their vechicle from a list 
6. The game could go indefinitely and let the user enter their name if they beat the previous high score 
7. The user can use any controller they want 
8. The user could be able to design their own level 
9. The game could be connected to the internet so users can upload the levels they make
10. Users can download other users levels 
